{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5f6b66722d","title":"对贺诚关于召开第二届全国卫生会议的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4d8d7b3b60","index":0,"year":1952,"month":11,"day":26,"articleId":"5f6b66722d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"7af178d2d0","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5f6b66722d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"贺诚，当时任中央人民政府卫生部副部长。"},{"id":"443611d139","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5f6b66722d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指为第二届全国卫生会议的题词。毛泽东题词的全文是：“动员起来，讲究卫生，减少疾病，提高健康水平，粉碎敌人的细菌战争。”"},{"id":"582ce8a4b2","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5f6b66722d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指定于1952年12月上旬召开的第二届全国卫生会议。这次会议拟总结爱国卫生运动及三年来卫生建设情况，并评奖爱国卫生运动模范，举办带有评比性的卫生展览。"},{"id":"ca223aa22a","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5f6b66722d","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"习仲勋，当时任中共中央宣传部部长、政务院文化教育委员会副主任。胡乔木，当时任中共中央宣传部副部长、政务院文化教育委员会秘书长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f5ddaf86f1","type":"title","text":"对贺诚\"关于召开第二届全国卫生会议的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5f6b66722d"},{"id":"7af178d2d0","type":"paragraph","text":"贺诚同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5f6b66722d"},{"id":"443611d139","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）题词时可写，请你们拟出几个简单语句送我择书；（二）此次会议准备工作甚为重要，应和习仲勋、胡乔木同志商药，并在文委党组加以讨论","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5f6b66722d"},{"id":"582ce8a4b2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5f6b66722d"},{"id":"ca223aa22a","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿六日","index":